divs: sighting detailsi was outside my school area at the back of the school when i saw 6 black right angle shaped figures(3 dimensional) in the sky 3 on top of three they had one white light on each corner then 2 jets where going towards the triangels and they shot up into the air, the jets went up as if to follw them. it happend fast. i am not sure what made me notice them, i guess it was just there. i told my mother but she said it was probably the airshow doing some last minute practices. however, she just realized that the airshow is not until oct. 16 & 17 of this year (2010). i have tried looking on the internet to see if i find similar objects.my friend *(name deleted--cms\sg) was there with me but he had his back to it. i asked him if he had seen it and he said no. **(wit's name deleted--cms\sg).
